shad Nadeem was welcomed in an extraordinary manner; his plane was given a water cannon salute,\\\" Tarar noted.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arshad Nadeem\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"an extraordinary manner\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"his plane\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"a water cannon salute\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarar\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The minister informed that Nadeem is scheduled to arrive at Islamabad's Nur Khan Airbase at 5pm via a special Pakistan Air Force aircraft and will be escorted with full state protocol.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.37677578518124e-20, \"text\": \"Islamabad\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\"}, {\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Air_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.420355840194968e-24, \"text\": \"Pakistan Air Force\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Air_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Air_Force\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The minister\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 869}, {\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"5pm\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"full state protocol\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Prime Minister's House has organized a banquet in honour of Arshad Nadeem, whom Tarar described as \\\"a beacon of inspiration for the youth.\\\"\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.5696853631705063, \"rank\": 0