 hometo bestow honours upon him, calling it \\\"a commendable gesture.\\\"\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1343, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provincial_Assembly_of_the_Punjab\", \"score\": 0.9999147731882099, \"rank\": 8.523407593377375e-05, \"text\": \"Punjab\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provincial_Assembly_of_the_Punjab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provincial_Assembly_of_the_Punjab\"}, {\"begin\": 1365, \"end\": 1377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryam_Nawaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maryam Nawaz\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryam_Nawaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryam_Nawaz\"}, {\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.9934085430122968, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The minister\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"a commendable gesture\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discussing the Independence Day celebrations, Tarar revealed that a major event is planned in Islamabad's F-9 Park, organised under the directives of PM Shehbaz.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.37677578518124e-20, \"text\": \"Islamabad\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Independence Day celebrations\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarar\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"a major event\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"the directives\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1625}, {\"ngram\": \"PM Shehbaz\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ministry of Information and Broadcasting will host Pakistan's first drone show, featuring 500 drones.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9877481687673744, \"rank\": 0.012403800502920687, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Ministry\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"Information\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"Broadcasting\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"500 drones\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This event will be non-political, focusing solely on the national flag and promoting patriotism,\\\" he emphasized.\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This event\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"the national flag\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"patriotism\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New visa policy The information minister also announced the launch of a new visa policy, simplifying the process for visitors from 126 countries.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"New visa policy\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"The information minister\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1904}, {\"ngram\": \"the launch\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1930}, {\"ngram\": \"a new visa policy\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"126 countries\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained, \\\"The visa fee for these countries has been abolished, and the application process has been made significantly easier.\\\"\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The visa fee\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"these countries\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"the application process\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He detailed that a simple form with 30 questions will allow applicants to quickly obtain a 90-day visa.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a simple form\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2176}, {\"ngram\": \"30 questions\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"applicants\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2216}, {\"ngram\": \"a 90-day visa\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He further stated, \\\"Gulf country residents will also be able to obtain a visa on arrival with just a passport.\\\"\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gulf country residents\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"a visa\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2328}, {\"ngram\": \"arrival\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2339}, {\"ngram\": \"just a passport\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regarding tourism, Tarar assured that security for incoming tourists is a top priority, with the Ministry of Interior coordinating closely with provincial governments to ensure the best possible arrangements.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tourism\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarar\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"incoming tourists\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"a top priority\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2450}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ministry\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\"