urce, and we want the world to come and see it,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 3075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Allah\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2969}, {\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2993}, {\"ngram\": \"every possible resource\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3022}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"COMMENTS Comments are moderated and generally will be posted if they are on-topic and not abusive.\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"COMMENTS Comments\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3094}, {\"ngram\": \"topic\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information, please see ourComments FAQ This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten, redistributed or derived from.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"ourComments\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3222}, {\"ngram\": \"FAQ\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"This material\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unless otherwise stated, all content is copyrighted \\u00a9 2025 The Express Tribune.\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all content\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3373}, {\"ngram\": \"The Express Tribune\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3415}]}]}"